      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/french-business-lobby-slams-le-pen-and-left-as-danger-to-economy</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国商业游说团体 Medef 的负责人批评了极右翼和左翼政党联盟的竞选计划，称它们对经济构成了威胁。]]></description>
