    <item>
      <title>工党有望赢得 162 个议席，MRP 民意调查发现更多共同点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/labour-set-for-162-seat-majority-more-in-common-mrp-poll-finds</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据“More in Common”民意调查显示，基尔·斯塔默领导的工党将在下个月的英国大选中获得 162 个席位的多数席位，这是最新预测，表明保守党首相里希·苏纳克将在 15 天后的投票后被赶下台。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-19/labour-set-for-162-seat-majority-more-in-common-mrp-poll-finds</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 19 Jun 2024 15:39:24 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
